metadata.name: AInfected God
metadata.description: Capturing a legion of tainted and ferocious deities, affected by an enigmatic infection. These divine beings defy conventional expectations, embodying a distorted appearance and erratic nature. This AI-generated collection, brimming with originality, is designed to enthrall enthusiasts who seek the unconventional and the cutting-edge. Each piece in this assemblage is a singular portrayal of the tumultuous and unforeseen essence of these celestial entities.
